entries.title_d: We have the Rebel pilot in custody, but she refuses to talk. Maybe if we kill enough of her friends, her tongue will loosen.
entries.title: Dathomir System: Destroy a Squad of Rebel Fighters
entries.quest_location_d: Destroy a designated Rebel squadron in the Dathomir system.
entries.quest_escort_d: Destroy all ships in the Rebel squadron. Make sure none escape.
entries.failed_escape: You let them escape! Return to the station for further instructions. Hopefully, we'll try again.
entries.destroy_escort: The entire squad must be eradicated.
entries.assassinate_success: Good work, pilot. Perhaps now our captured Rebel pilot will be more inclined to talk.
entries.arrival_phase_2: Nav location to the target squad has been located. Proceed with extreme prejudice.
entries.arrival_phase_1: Scanning system for a Rebel squadron. Stand by to proceed with the attack.
